  "Mia earns $3,500/month. She identifies $450/month in wants she can eliminate: unused gym ($40), extra streaming ($35), daily specialty coffee ($125), and impulse shopping ($250). If she invests this amount monthly at 7% for 20 years, approximately how much will she accumulate?": "",
